\hat{f}(\xi)
I=[-\frac{1}{2},\frac{1}{2}]
f(x) = \sum^{\infty}_{n=-\infty} f(n)K(x-n)
K(y) = \frac{sin( \pi y)}{\pi y}
\hat{f(\xi)} = \chi_I(\xi) \sum^{\infty}_{n=-\infty} f(n)e^{-2 \pi i n \xi}
\chi
{K}(\xi) = \hat{\chi}_I(\xi) 
1 = e^{-2 \pi i n \xi}e^{-2 \pi i(x-n) \xi}
